div.p:


AND no doubt, One great End and Motive must be the same with others of his wondrous Works; 
                     viz.

                  To show his glorious Power, Being & Presence, and to excite the Sons of Men to admire & honour Him. For these great Operations of Providence having a just and natural Tendency to produce such proper Conceptions & Excitements in us; they must needs be some of His Ends & Motives in them.
